{"tid":2007800,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[白票熱狗五毛乘機進攻]fc:今日李慧琼可以趕11位民主派出會議室，與2011年泛民支持嘅《議事規則》修訂無關。","createTime":"2020-05-08T14:16:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T15:02:56.000Z","uid":38795,"like":14,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4af1196c814db08c8b91384a7f3d770bdc06631e","tid":2007800,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:16:36.000Z","msg":"2011年嘅《議事規則》修訂係將只有立法會主席、常設或專責委員會主席，可驅逐行為不檢議員離場的權力下放至其他委員會（例如事務委員會）。<br />\n<br />\n內務委員會（是常設委員會，財委會亦然）主席係一直都可以趕人出會議室，2011年之前已經有呢個權力。<br />\n<br />\n今日李慧琼可以趕11位民主派出會議室，與2011年泛民支持嘅《議事規則》修訂無關。"},{"pid":"4e0478f2859f9eaff2f13b942f832e0953aa7542","tid":2007800,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:19:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628dd656b100457feb4a2b4b2776c73e23a58f58","tid":2007800,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"親熱派 : &quot;販民黃絲豬又做騷！&quot;"},{"pid":"937590d57f65b61662acbb2387120e2867b97c8d","tid":2007800,"uid":38795,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"628dd656b100457feb4a2b4b2776c73e23a58f58","tid":2007800,"uid":70487,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"親熱派 : &quot;販民黃絲豬又做騷！&quot;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:21:55.000Z","msg":"其實係中聯辦員工"},{"pid":"b7a14751b568187b5a771530e39129be0f3d6fac","tid":2007800,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"